quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  20,13,aur mein ne tum ko intikhab karliya hai to jo hukum diya jaye usay suno
  20,14,be shak mein hi khuda hon. mere siwa koi mabood nahi to meri ibadat karo aur meri yaad ke liye namaz parha karo
  20,15,qayamat yaqeenan anay wali hai. mein chahta hon ke is ( ke waqt ) ko posheeda rakhon taakay har shakhs jo koshish kere is ka badla paye
  20,16,to jo shakhs is par imaan nahi rakhta aur apni khwahish ke peechay chalta hai ( kahin ) tum ko is ( ke yaqeen ) se rok nah day to ( is soorat mein ) tum halaak hojao
  20,17,aur moose yeh tumahray dahinay haath meinkiya hai
  20,18,unhon ne kaha yeh meri laathi hai. is par mein sahara lagaata hon aur is se apni bakrion ke liye pattay jharta hon aur is mein mere liye aur bhi kayi faiday hain
  20,19,farmaya ke moose usay daal do
  20,20,to unhon ne is ko daal diya aur woh nagahan saanp ban kar dornay laga
  20,21,khuda ne farmaya ke usay pakar lau aur darna mat. hum is ko abhi is ki pehli haalat par lota den ge
  20,22,aur apna haath apni baghal se lagalo woh kisi aib ( o bemari ) ke baghair safaid ( chamakta dmkta ) niklay ga. ( yeh ) doosri nishani ( hai )
  20,23,taakay hum tumhe apne nishanaat azeem deikhein
  20,24,tum firaon ke paas jao ( ke ) woh sarkash ho raha hai
  20,25,kaha mere perwar-digaar ( is kaam ke liye ) mera seenah khol day
  20,26,aur mera kaam aasaan kardey
  20,27,aur meri zabaan ki girah khol day
  20,28,taakay woh baat samajh len
  20,29,aur mere ghar walon mein se ( aik ko ) mera wazeer ( yani madadgaar ) muqarrar farma
  20,30,( yani ) mere bhai Haroon ko
  20,31,is se meri qowat ko mazboot farma
  20,32,aur usay mere kaam mein shareek kar
  20,33,taakay hum teri bohat si tasbeeh karen
  20,34,aur tujhe kasrat se yaad karen
  20,35,to hum ko ( har haal mein ) dekh raha hai
  20,36,farmaya moose tumhari dua qubool ki gayi
  20,37,aur hum ne tum par aik baar aur bhi ahsaankiya tha
